# Backend Architecture

Backend NestJS 10 + Fastify adapter. Prisma 5 ORM. Her modül standardize klasör yapısı izler.

## Modül Klasör Yapısı

```
apps/api/src/<module>/
├── <module>.controller.ts       # HTTP routes
├── <module>.service.ts          # Business logic
├── <module>.module.ts           # DI wiring
├── <module>.exceptions.ts       # Domain exceptions
├── dto/                         # Request/response DTOs (types from shared-schemas)
│   ├── create-<entity>.dto.ts
│   └── update-<entity>.dto.ts
├── guards/                      # Module-specific guards (if needed)
├── decorators/                  # Module-specific decorators (if needed)
└── <module>.service.test.ts     # Unit tests (co-located)
```

Module-level test'ler `apps/api/test/<module>.integration.test.ts` altında.

## Module Registration

Her modül kendi `Module` sınıfını export eder:

```typescript
@Module({
  imports: [PrismaModule, RedisModule],
  controllers: [UsersController],
  providers: [UsersService, UsersRepository],
  exports: [UsersService],  // başka modüllerde kullanılacaksa
})
export class UsersModule {}
```

`AppModule` tüm modülleri import eder:

```typescript
@Module({
  imports: [
    ConfigModule.forRoot({ isGlobal: true }),
    PrismaModule,
    RedisModule,
    AuthModule,
    UsersModule,
    RolesModule,
    // ...
  ],
  providers: [
    { provide: APP_GUARD, useClass: JwtAuthGuard },
    { provide: APP_GUARD, useClass: PermissionGuard },
    { provide: APP_GUARD, useClass: CsrfGuard },
    { provide: APP_INTERCEPTOR, useClass: AuditInterceptor },
    { provide: APP_INTERCEPTOR, useClass: ResponseEnvelopeInterceptor },
    { provide: APP_FILTER, useClass: GlobalExceptionFilter },
  ],
})
export class AppModule {}
```

Global guards/interceptors/filters `AppModule` provider'larında register edilir.

## Response Envelope (Global Interceptor)

Tüm success response'lar standardize envelope:

```typescript
{
  success: true,
  data: <actual response>
}
```

`ResponseEnvelopeInterceptor` otomatik sarar — controller sadece `data` kısmını return eder:

```typescript
@Get(':id')
async findById(@Param('id') id: string) {
  return this.usersService.findById(id);  // Service UserResponse döner, interceptor envelope ekler
}
```

Pagination için:

```typescript
{
  success: true,
  data: {
    items: [...],
    pagination: {
      nextCursor: "...",
      hasMore: true,
      limit: 20
    }
  }
}
```

## Error Response Format

Error response envelope:

```typescript
{
  success: false,
  error: {
    code: 'USER_SICIL_DUPLICATE',
    message: 'Bu sicil zaten kayıtlı',
    details: { sicil: '12345678' }  // opsiyonel, context-specific
  }
}
```

`GlobalExceptionFilter` typed exception'ları bu formata map eder.

## Exception Hierarchy

```typescript
// apps/api/src/common/exceptions/app.exception.ts
export class AppException extends Error {
  constructor(
    public readonly code: string,
    public readonly message: string,
    public readonly httpStatus: number,
    public readonly details?: Record<string, unknown>,
  ) {
    super(message);
  }
}
```

Module-specific exception'lar `AppException`'dan extend eder:

```typescript
// apps/api/src/users/users.exceptions.ts
export class UserSicilDuplicateException extends AppException {
  constructor(sicil?: string) {
    super(
      'USER_SICIL_DUPLICATE',
      'Bu sicil zaten kayıtlı',
      409,
      sicil ? { sicil } : undefined,
    );
  }
}

export class UserNotFoundException extends AppException {
  constructor() {
    super('USER_NOT_FOUND', 'Kullanıcı bulunamadı', 404);
  }
}

export class UserManagerCycleException extends AppException {
  constructor() {
    super('USER_MANAGER_CYCLE', 'Yönetici atamasında döngü tespit edildi', 422);
  }
}
```

Global filter exception'ı yakalar, error envelope'a map eder, HTTP status set eder.

## Dependency Injection

Constructor injection zorunlu. Field injection yok. Opsiyonel dependency `@Optional()`:

```typescript
@Injectable()
export class FeatureService {
  constructor(
    private readonly prisma: PrismaService,
    private readonly eventEmitter: EventEmitter2,
    @Optional() private readonly metrics?: MetricsService,
  ) {}
}
```

Circular dependency varsa refactor et — shared logic'i üçüncü service'e çıkar. `forwardRef` son çare.

## Common Module

`apps/api/src/common/` cross-cutting:

```
common/
├── decorators/
│   ├── public.decorator.ts
│   ├── current-user.decorator.ts
│   ├── require-permission.decorator.ts
│   └── audit.decorator.ts
├── exceptions/
│   └── app.exception.ts          # base class
├── filters/
│   └── global-exception.filter.ts
├── interceptors/
│   ├── response-envelope.interceptor.ts
│   └── audit.interceptor.ts
├── pipes/
│   └── zod-validation.pipe.ts
├── encryption/
│   └── encryption.service.ts
└── common.module.ts
```

`CommonModule` `@Global()` işaretli — her yerde kullanılır.

## Controllers — Thin

Controller minimal iş yapar:
- Route tanımı
- Decorator'lar (permission, validation, rate limit)
- Service çağrısı
- Response

Business logic controller'da yer almaz:

```typescript
@Controller('users')
export class UsersController {
  constructor(private readonly usersService: UsersService) {}

  @Get()
  @RequirePermission(Permission.USER_LIST_VIEW)
  async list(
    @Query(new ZodValidationPipe(UserListQuerySchema)) query: UserListQuery,
    @CurrentUser() actor: AuthenticatedUser,
  ) {
    return this.usersService.findMany(query, actor);
  }

  @Post()
  @RequirePermission(Permission.USER_CREATE)
  async create(
    @Body(new ZodValidationPipe(CreateUserSchema)) dto: CreateUserInput,
    @CurrentUser() actor: AuthenticatedUser,
  ) {
    return this.usersService.create(dto, actor);
  }
}
```

## Services — Fat

Tüm business logic service'te. Pattern detay `apps/api/**/*.service.ts` rule'unda (auto-attach).

## Repository Layer (Opsiyonel)

Basit modüller için Prisma Client direkt service'te kullanılır. Kompleks query'ler için `<module>.repository.ts`:

```typescript
@Injectable()
export class UsersRepository {
  constructor(private readonly prisma: PrismaService) {}

  async findByCompanyWithFilters(filters: UserFilters) {
    return this.prisma.users.findMany({
      where: this.buildWhereClause(filters),
      include: { roles: true, company: true },
    });
  }
}
```

MVP'de repository çoğu modül için overkill — service direkt Prisma'yı kullanır.

## Config Management

`@nestjs/config` ile. `.env.local` dev, AWS Secrets Manager staging/prod.

```typescript
// apps/api/src/config/config.schema.ts
export const ConfigSchema = z.object({
  NODE_ENV: z.enum(['development', 'staging', 'production']),
  DATABASE_URL: z.string().url(),
  REDIS_URL: z.string().url(),
  JWT_ACCESS_SECRET_CURRENT: z.string().min(32),
  // ...
});

export type Config = z.infer<typeof ConfigSchema>;
```

Config boot-time'da validate edilir. Invalid config → startup fail (fail-fast).

## Logging (Pino)

Structured JSON logging:

```typescript
private readonly logger = new Logger(UsersService.name);

async create(input, actor) {
  this.logger.log({
    event: 'user.create.started',
    actorId: actor.id,
    input: { sicil: input.sicil },  // PII dikkat: password, token yasak
  });
  // ...
}
```

Sensitive field'lar redaction ile loglara girmez (Pino redaction config).

## Banned Patterns

- Controller'da Prisma query (service layer bypass)
- Inline error response (`throw new BadRequestException('...')` yerine typed exception)
- `any` type
- Promise.all içinde error swallowing (explicit `Promise.allSettled` + handle)
- `@Injectable({ scope: Scope.REQUEST })` gereksiz yere (default singleton yeter)
- Manuel transaction management (Prisma `$transaction` callback kullan)

